    path('<int:pk>/delete/', views.event_delete, name='event_delete'),
    path('<int:pk>/', views.event_detail, name='event_detail'),
]
```

You can now include these `urls.py` files into your project's main `urls.py` using `include()` to make the views accessible through the browser.

